snippet.title: Absylon 7 - Sergo's Story Gameplay
snippet.description: A 15-minute gameplay video that tells the story of Sergo, the game's protagonist. You will learn how he got into the Absylon science complexes, as well as get acquainted with the first mechanics of the game.
